Animaster is a free animation library aimed at making your web development process easier.

Arguments:
speed - fast/medium/slow/veryfast/veryslow
opacity - 0-100/100-0/100-50/0-50
pixels - 20/40/60/80/100


Syntax: animation-(opacity|pixels|degrees) speed
e.g: flyinleft speed-fast

List of animations:

Hover Effects: 
zoomin
zoomout
floatup
floatdown
floatleft
floatright
pulse
bob
bgleftfill
bgrightfill
bgfade
borderfade
unblur
blur
ungrayscale
grayscale
blurgrayscale
unblurgrayscale
glow
buttonarrow | USE: <button class="buttonarrow-speed" style=""><span>Hover </span></button>


Event Effects:
opacity-speed-opacity
flyinleft-speed
flyinleft-speed-pixels
flyinright-speed
flyinright-speed-pixels
spin-speed
spinonce-speed